Naming convention:

class Name => start with upper case
Employee
MyFirstDemo

Variable/method => camel notation start with lower case
eg:
num1
num2
hra
myFirstVariable

constant variable/Enum element  => UPPER case
PI
FIXED_AMOUNT
MY_FIRST_CONSTANT_VARIABLE



Method Overloading:
method with same name and different signature.
it doesn't depend upon return type.

Signatue:
1. no of parameter
2. type of parameter
3. sequence in which parameter passed








Enhanced for loop:
for(elementType var  :collection){

}


2d array
int[][] arr= new int[2][3];  //y
int[][] barr= new int[2][];  //y
int[][] carr = new int[][3];  //n
int[][] darr = new int[][];





